Package arduino.move

This package contains classes the represent finger moves and servo moves.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FingerMove
    This class represents a servo move.
    HandMove
    Represents a hand move as a list of finger moves.
    HandMoveSequence
    Represents a sequence of hand moves.
    Move
    This class represents a move.
    PositionMove
    This move represents a position move.
    SensorMove
    This move represents a sensor move.
    ServoMove
    This class represents a servo move.
